{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/tlsconnectionprotocol\/onnotifyusesystemcertdb(flags:handler:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TLSConnectionProtocol"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotifyUseSystemCertdb","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"TLSConnectionRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO16TLSConnectionRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TLSConnectionRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}]}],"name":"flags"},{"name":"handler","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notifyUseSystemCertdb"},{"text":" signal is emitted","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"